  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThere are 2 places where account can be renamed and both have different rules.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nWallet view edit\r\n1. Go to wallet screen\r\n2. Right click `Status account` -> Press edit\r\n3. Try add any character or just add space.\r\n\r\nSettings edit\r\n1. Go to settings -> Wallet\r\n2. Press any account\r\n3. Click edit icon\r\n4. Spaces and special characters can be added\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nWallet account rename is consistent through whole application\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/11396062/fe821aba-6979-497f-8ef0-1fbac9120f0e)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version:  master\r\n\r\n",
