    "body": "There is one more place where you can set an account name, that's when you're adding it, but basically add account popup and edit account popup from the wallet section share the same logic, which by my opinion should be the correct one, cause that's what figma says about requirements.\r\n\r\nWallet settings part is not redone yet to align with new wallet settings part designed in fimga, so once that's done it will be the same.\r\n\r\nBut one thing more which we should check is what are the set requirements in mobile app (if they are not the same we are in a problem again).",
